{"tid":2031264,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"兄弟努力 各自爬山","createTime":"2020-05-23T09:42:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T14:11:01.000Z","uid":359022,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cc25a5a942a25f52ba666cc961a4fc98e439fdec","tid":2031264,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:42:52.000Z","msg":"遊行港島逼爆畫面真係好靚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n524 527 會唔會係一個機會<br />\n話比全世界人聽香港人係熱愛自由和平嘅一個種族<br />\n非ccp強扣帽子下嘅恐怖份子？<br />\n<br />\n記得第一次組人鏈都係好靚、超級感動<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以黎嘅人鏈變奏版-2m距離，自發各有各舉牌-反對惡安法，兩制已亡，恆指肚瀉，etc<br />\n<br />\n呢個係和平嘅方式和平嘅象徵。<br />\n<br />\n假若呢個、合情合法合理嘅抗爭都受到打壓，<br />\n<br />\n真正嘅恐怖主義全球必定心中有數。<br />\n<br />\n525我地又可以得到彈藥猛攻輿論戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n狗狗票控嘅畫面都會好好睇：保持兩米距離抄牌，老銅抄到去獅子山頂再返回彌敦道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係罰到2000？我有d保留<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對比外國反家居隔離令嘅示威，我地和平理性得多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或者有人會話而家組人鏈時間倉促<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用番舊劇本就得啦<br />\n狗狗重倉猝啦，大部分狗力集中曬西環<br />\n暴徒又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人最鍾意排隊，排隊係我地嘅國技<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2m人鏈陣勢 vs 惡安法<br />\n<br />\n究竟最終勝利者會係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\np牌仔一日quota已完，絞盡腦汁的一個爬山方法，同意就幫幫忙輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw，吹雞填問卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌晒你地老母!又話打國際線???民記出左國安法survey冇人講???<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2030351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2030351</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n標題開得衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71046c053218484b8215f788d6cfe838c36bde31","tid":2031264,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:43:27.000Z","msg":"各爬自山"},{"pid":"89a0696e52b30badf02d37c5b306762bad7e2139","tid":2031264,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:44:21.000Z","msg":"極速負皮，說明什麼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b345e320496a2fb77055c73658f8852623e1fb54","tid":2031264,"uid":108462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:45:24.000Z","msg":"叫香港人俾2000蚊去抗爭慘過叫佢地做中共隻狗<br />\n到呢刻都可以拗送唔送頭 <br />\n轉職奶共咪唔洗送囉 屌！"},{"pid":"a9d462672119328932e48447dbeac68d42eca4c2","tid":2031264,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:46:22.000Z","msg":"我鍾意排排企<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d388ef92ec361ae87a17c16a074a671822e585","tid":2031264,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b345e320496a2fb77055c73658f8852623e1fb54","tid":2031264,"uid":108462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:45:24.000Z","msg":"叫香港人俾2000蚊去抗爭慘過叫佢地做中共隻狗<br />\n到呢刻都可以拗送唔送頭 <br />\n轉職奶共咪唔洗送囉 屌！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:47:07.000Z","msg":"2000蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />罰得到先至奇"},{"pid":"cf763e134384188934be46fd3abda5dee2d0b735","tid":2031264,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9d462672119328932e48447dbeac68d42eca4c2","tid":2031264,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:46:22.000Z","msg":"我鍾意排排企<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:47:28.000Z","msg":"我去到邊都鍾意企係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1182b1a2c90dd0609eed55620a2f22f1d4956398","tid":2031264,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf763e134384188934be46fd3abda5dee2d0b735","tid":2031264,"uid":359022,"like":0,"