nail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fai0ugyc.jpg&h=67090f5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b80c2d1d19b723c2a4ff40a581aacab3d4ae1d7","tid":2031264,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T10:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bZG9gym.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbZG9gym.png&h=454c521e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1c2ec9012a26cdfdde43266445ffddb725e612e","tid":2031264,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T11:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBe water my friends<br />\n<br />\n和平理性自由有創意<br />\n係香港人特質<br />\n<br />\n使出香港人大技，破佢老母限聚令<br />\n 排排企人鏈，保持兩米距離<br />\n1000人、10000人、100000人、1000000人<br />\n抄佢老母標、抄到佢天荒地老<br />\n彌敦道出九龍大老山隧道獅子山入口再出港島太平山<br />\n同我罰抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抄到無紙<br />\n<br />\n呃佢老母ot錢<br />\n<br />\n法庭忙到甩轆<br />\n最後原來得個吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜都唔洗罰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鍾意講咩玩咩都係自由意志<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc21684c97266858070c3f9dd1c1a3a1051f1296","tid":2031264,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T11:24:13.000Z","msg":"[民記国安法民調要人] 依家有4萬6千人做咗 想去到10萬人以上<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2031362\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2031362</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im